&lt;p data-start=&quot;490&quot; data-end=&quot;854&quot;&gt;Achievers Early College Prep (AECP) is New Jersey’s first public charter school serving both middle and high school students through an innovative &lt;strong data-start=&quot;637&quot; data-end=&quot;678&quot;&gt;early college and STEAM-focused model&lt;/strong&gt;. Our mission is to ensure students graduate with strong academic mastery, college credits, industry credentials, and the skills needed to succeed in college, career, and life.&lt;/p&gt;
