&lt;p data-start=&quot;118&quot; data-end=&quot;202&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;118&quot; data-end=&quot;132&quot;&gt;Job Title:&lt;/strong&gt; Pre-Nursing Teacher&lt;br data-start=&quot;152&quot; data-end=&quot;155&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;155&quot; data-end=&quot;170&quot;&gt;Reports To:&lt;/strong&gt; Principal / Academic Director&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;204&quot; data-end=&quot;707&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;204&quot; data-end=&quot;226&quot;&gt;Position Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;226&quot; data-end=&quot;229&quot;&gt;The Pre-Nursing Teacher will provide high-quality instruction to high school students enrolled in the pre-nursing pathway. This teacher will prepare students with foundational knowledge and practical skills necessary for success in nursing programs and healthcare-related fields. The ideal candidate will have a strong background in health sciences, experience in nursing or a related healthcare field, and a passion for teaching and mentoring future healthcare professionals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;709&quot; data-end=&quot;736&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;709&quot; data-end=&quot;734&quot;&gt;Key Responsibilities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul data-start=&quot;737&quot; data-end=&quot;1788&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;737&quot; data-end=&quot;871&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;739&quot; data-end=&quot;871&quot;&gt;Develop and deliver engaging, standards-aligned lessons in health science, anatomy, physiology, and introductory nursing concepts.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;872&quot; data-end=&quot;989&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;874&quot; data-end=&quot;989&quot;&gt;Provide students with hands-on learning opportunities, including demonstrations, simulations, and lab activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;990&quot; data-end=&quot;1134&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;992&quot; data-end=&quot;1134&quot;&gt;Teach foundational clinical skills (e.g., vital signs, infection control, patient care basics) in preparation for further nursing education.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1135&quot; data-end=&quot;1267&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1137&quot; data-end=&quot;1267&quot;&gt;Prepare students for certifications (e.g., CPR, First Aid, CNA if applicable) and guide them through healthcare career pathways.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1268&quot; data-end=&quot;1364&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1270&quot; data-end=&quot;1364&quot;&gt;Collaborate with colleagues to align curriculum with college and career readiness standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1365&quot; data-end=&quot;1453&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1367&quot; data-end=&quot;1453&quot;&gt;Monitor and assess student progress, providing feedback and interventions as needed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1454&quot; data-end=&quot;1563&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1456&quot; data-end=&quot;1563&quot;&gt;Maintain high expectations for student achievement, professionalism, and ethical standards in healthcare.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1564&quot; data-end=&quot;1664&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1566&quot; data-end=&quot;1664&quot;&gt;Create a supportive classroom environment that fosters student engagement, inquiry, and respect.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1665&quot; data-end=&quot;1788&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1667&quot; data-end=&quot;1788&quot;&gt;Build partnerships with local healthcare providers, colleges, and programs to support student growth and opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;
